<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= subject %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 5px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        h1 { color: #fcfcfc; }
        p { margin: 10px 0; }
        blockquote { background-color: #f0f0f0; border-left: 5px solid #005f5a; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        a { color: #005f5a; text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .container { font-size: 16px; }
        .container p { margin: 10px 0; }
        .header { background-color: #005f5a; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1><%=subject%></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%=name%></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for contacting us regarding "<%=subject%>".</p>
            <p>We've received your message and will get back to you shortly.</p>
            <p>For your records, here's a summary of your inquiry:</p>
            <blockquote>
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%=subject%></p>
                <p><strong>Recipient:</strong> <%=name%></p>
                <p><strong>Message:</strong> <%=message%></p>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%=year%> Lucid petro chemical. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>